Class AbstractQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • queues.AbstractQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Node>, Queue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FCFSQueue, LCFSQueue, MPFQueue, SJFQueue

    public abstract class AbstractQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue
    Represents a queue at Pat and Mat's restaurant. Abstract method enqueue(Customer customer) must be overridden by a subclass depending on the approach taken to attend customers.
    Author:
    Bryan J Sanchez
